        <mxCell id="impl" value="Implemented (Tiers 0–2): clients/flash/client.ts (typed REST), clients/flash-ref.ts (live price/band keeper), tests/hedge-demo.ts. Off-chain composition — never inside run_batch, so N1 holds. Flash leg mocked on devnet (mainnet-only); FLASH_LIVE=1 = real preview." style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e6f4ea;strokeColor=#38763d;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=8;verticalAlign=middle;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="80" y="500" width="960" height="50" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
